Privacy Policy for GPT Sharing API

Last Updated: [Date]

1. Introduction

Welcome to our GPT Sharing API. Your privacy is important to us. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our service.

2. Information We Collect

Input Data: We collect and temporarily store the prompts you provide to generate responses.
Generated Responses: We do not store the generated responses unless explicitly requested for troubleshooting or service improvement.
Usage Data: We collect usage data such as API call frequency, response times, and errors for service monitoring and optimization.
3. How We Use Your Information

To provide and improve our GPT services.
To monitor and analyze usage and trends to enhance user experience.
4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not share your data with third parties except in the following cases:

Compliance with legal obligations.
Prevention of fraud and abuse.
5. Data Security

We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access.

6. Your Rights

You have the right to access and delete your data upon request.
You can opt-out of data collection by not using the service.
7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on this page.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at [contact email].
